<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.258733>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Habitus of Apolygus spp. A: Apolygus rubrifasciatus Kim et Jung, sp. nov. Holotype ♂; B: Apolygus atriclavus Kim et Jung, sp. nov. Holotype ♂; C: ditto, Paratype ♀. Scale bar: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/258733/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.258734>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Male genitalia of Apolygus spp. A – E: Apolygus rubrifasciatus Kim et Jung, sp. nov.; F – J: Apolygus atriclavus Kim et Jung, sp. nov.; A, F: left paramere; B, C, G, H: right paramere; D, E, I, J: vesica; ns: needle – shaped spicule; ms: median sclerite; vsc: ventral sclerite; ws: wing – shaped sclerite; sls: sublateral sclerite; ls: lateral sclerite. Scale bar 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/258734/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.258735>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Live adult of Apolygus atriclavus Kim et Jung, sp. nov. on Artemisia selengensis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/258735/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

